<paragraph blockId="2.[139,790,1039,1928]" lastBlockId="2.[827,1479,282,1170]" pageId="2" pageNumber="313">
Las variedades de Chodat en 
<emphasis box="[486,657,1039,1063]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="313">
<taxonomicName box="[486,648,1039,1063]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Telanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="313" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosea">Telanthera rosea</taxonomicName>
:
</emphasis>
tardíamente en 1927, Chodat se da cuenta que debe considerar 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Telanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="313" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosea">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="313">Telanthera rosea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
como una variedad de 
<emphasis box="[439,665,1103,1127]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="313">
<taxonomicName box="[439,661,1103,1127]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Alternanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="313" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hirtula">Alternanthera hirtula</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Al efectuar la nueva combinación 
<taxonomicName authority=", Chodat" authorityName="Chodat" box="[379,672,1135,1159]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Alternanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="313" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="hirtula" variety="rosea">
<emphasis box="[379,478,1135,1159]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="313">A. hirtula</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis box="[528,585,1136,1159]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="313">rosea,</emphasis>
Chodat
</taxonomicName>
incluye en 
<taxonomicName box="[139,240,1167,1191]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Alternanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="313" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hirtula">
<emphasis box="[139,240,1167,1191]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="313">A. hirtula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
el conjunto de las 4 variedades descritas por él en 
<emphasis box="[139,321,1199,1223]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="313">
<taxonomicName box="[139,310,1199,1223]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Telanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="313" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rosea">Telanthera rosea</taxonomicName>
:
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Chodat" authorityYear="1901" box="[329,598,1200,1223]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Telanthera" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="2" pageNumber="313" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="rosea" variety="atropurpurea">
